The '''Kuati Security Forces''' was the [[Law enforcement agency/Legends|police]] force of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Kuat/Legends|Kuat]].

==History==
Their organizational purpose was to stop crime on Kuat and maintain security in the [[Kuat system/Legends|Kuat system]].<ref name="CATCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

They patrolled the various orbiting [[Kuat Drive Yards/Legends|shipyards]] and outlying [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] stations. Some were implicated in dealings with [[Neimoidian/Legends|Neimoidian]] agents shortly before the [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|Battle of Geonosis]].<ref name="DCKF">{{DB|character|kalynfarnmir|Farnmir, Kalyn}}</ref>

Upon the creation of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], [[Kuat Drive Yards/Legends|Kuat Drive Yards]] found themselves busy with the construction fleets of Imperial Warships, and the Kuati Security Forces were augmented and Imperialized to increase security and ensure the warship-production. They were also tasked with guarding Kuat Drive Yards offices on Coruscant and many other Imperial worlds.<ref name="TFUCG">''[[The Force Unleashed Campaign Guide]]''</ref>

